import {
    IonHeader,
    IonPage,
    IonTitle,
    IonToolbar,
    IonContent,
    IonMenu,
    IonList,
    IonItem,
    IonRouterOutlet,
    IonMenuButton,
    IonButtons
} from '@ionic/react';
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';

const AdminLayout: React.FC = () => {
    return (
        <IonPage>
            <IonHeader>
                <IonToolbar>
                    <IonButtons slot="start">
                        <IonMenuButton menu="first"></IonMenuButton>
                    </IonButtons>

                    <IonTitle>Dashboard</IonTitle>

                </IonToolbar>
            </IonHeader>
            <IonMenu side="start" menuId="first" contentId="main">
                <IonHeader>
                    <IonToolbar color="medium">
                        <IonTitle>Dashboard</IonTitle>
                    </IonToolbar>
                </IonHeader>
                <IonContent>
                    <IonList>
                        <IonItem >Manage Article</IonItem>
                        <IonItem >Manage Group</IonItem>
                        <IonItem>Menu Item</IonItem>
                        <IonItem >logout</IonItem>
                    </IonList>
                </IonContent>
            </IonMenu>
            <IonRouterOutlet id="main"></IonRouterOutlet>


        </IonPage>
    );
}
export default AdminLayout;
